description: Product Description Designed for all dogs in mind! This toy is designed for all dogs, from puppies to large dogs and everything in between. We are confident they will all love it! Built to last! 1cm thick cotton rope and quality TPR rubber this toy should stand the test of time to become your dog's favorite toy! Pet safe! We understand the importance of your dogs safety with this in mind there is no fluff for you the owner to worry about! No boredom! This toy is packed with loads of uses from tug of war, fetch to filling it with their favorite treats this will keep your dog occupied for hours! Please Note : Please ensure this toy is suitable for your pets play preferences & size, remembering that no toy is completely indestructible. This toy is of a tougher construction for rougher play but it not indestructible and is not to be left with your dog to be used as a chew toy.
